NARRATIVE STRUCTURE ANALYSIS
Systematic breakdown of story architecture  
808.036 — Narrative Structure / Plot & Story Analysis / Literary Composition
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Narrative structure analysis treats a story as an engineered system:
events • time • perspective • causality • meaning.

